create table VLB_IMPORT_TMP ( a001 varchar(36), b244 varchar(15), b203 varchar(255), b036 varchar(255), b047 varchar(255), b069 varchar(5), b070 varchar(255), j151 varchar(15), j153 varchar(15) )
create unique index VLB_IMPORT_TMP_ID on VLB_IMPORT_TMP (a001)
CREATE TABLE XMLwithOpenXML ( Id INT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY, XMLData XML, LoadedDateTime DATETIME )

DECLARE @XML AS XML, @hDoc AS INT, @SQL NVARCHAR (MAX)
SELECT @XML = XMLData FROM XMLwithOpenXML
EXEC sp_xml_preparedocument @hDoc OUTPUT, @XML
insert into vlb_import_tmp (a001) Select a001 from openxml(@hDoc, 'ONIXmessage/product') with ( a001 [varchar] (36) 'a001' )
update VLB_IMPORT_TMP set b244= (select top 1 b244 from openxml(@hDoc, 'ONIXmessage/product/productidentifier') with (a001 [varchar] (36) '../a001', b221 [int] 'b221', b244 [varchar] (15) 'b244' ) as b where b221=15 and b.a001=a.a001) from vlb_import_tmp a
update VLB_IMPORT_TMP set b203= (Select top 1 b203 from openxml(@hDoc, 'ONIXmessage/product/title') with ( a001 [varchar] (36) '../a001', b203 [varchar](255) 'b203', b202 [varchar](2) 'b202' ) as b where b202='01' and b.a001=a.a001) from VLB_IMPORT_TMP a
update VLB_IMPORT_TMP set b036= (Select top 1 b036 from openxml(@hDoc, 'ONIXmessage/product/contributor') with ( a001 [varchar] (36) '../a001', b035 [varchar](5) 'b035', b036 [varchar](255) 'b036' ) as b where b035='A01' and b.a001=a.a001) from VLB_IMPORT_TMP a
update VLB_IMPORT_TMP set b047= (Select TOP 1 b047 from openxml(@hDoc, 'ONIXmessage/product/contributor') with ( a001 [varchar] (36) '../a001', b035 [varchar](5) 'b035', b047 [varchar](255) 'b047' ) as b where b035='A01' and b.a001=a.a001) from VLB_IMPORT_TMP a
update VLB_IMPORT_TMP set b069= (Select top 1 b069 from openxml(@hDoc, 'ONIXmessage/product/mainsubject') with ( a001 [varchar] (36) '../a001', b068 [varchar] (5) 'b068', b069 [varchar] (5) 'b069' ) as b where b068='2.0' and b.a001=a.a001) from VLB_IMPORT_TMP a
update VLB_IMPORT_TMP set b070= (Select top 1 b070 from openxml(@hDoc, 'ONIXmessage/product/mainsubject') with ( a001 [varchar] (36) '../a001', b068 [varchar] (5) 'b068', b070 [varchar] (255) 'b070' ) as b where b068='2.0' and b.a001=a.a001) from VLB_IMPORT_TMP a
update VLB_IMPORT_TMP set j151= (Select top 1 j151 from openxml(@hDoc, 'ONIXmessage/product/supplydetail/price') with ( a001 [varchar] (36) '../../a001', j151 [varchar] (15) 'j151', b251 [varchar] (255) 'b251' ) as b where b251='DE' and b.a001=a.a001) from VLB_IMPORT_TMP a
update VLB_IMPORT_TMP set j153= (Select top 1 j153 from openxml(@hDoc, 'ONIXmessage/product/supplydetail/price') with ( a001 [varchar] (36) '../../a001', j153 [varchar] (15) 'j153', b251 [varchar] (255) 'b251' ) as b where b251='DE' and b.a001=a.a001) from VLB_IMPORT_TMP a
EXEC sp_xml_removedocument @hDoc
